title: Carter Reaffirms Alliance as South Korean President, Defense Minister Visit Pentagon (US Department of Defense) ...
text: ( Source : US Department of Defense ) WASHINGTON, October 15 , 2015 - In a meeting with South Korea 's president and defense minister at the Pentagon today, Defense Secretary Ash Carter reaffirmed the strength of the U.S. -South Korean alliance
